Ivory Coast’s Gbagbo Captured by French Forces, Handed Over, Reuters Says

-- B y   P a u l   R i c h a r d s o n
-- 
2011-04-11T13:12:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-11/ivory-coast-s-gbagbo-captured-by-french-forces-handed-over-reuters-says.html
Ivory Coast ’s former president,
 Laurent Gbagbo , has been captured by French special forces and
handed over to opposition leaders, Reuters reported, citing an
unidentified adviser to Gbagbo.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
